ygData.messageBody:
On Wed, Oct 27/99, James <manickd@...> wrote:
> From: "James" <manickd@...>
>
> Im level 32 now! Not too sure where to fight or what to kill. If any one has
> any clue that would be great. To be honest I know of lower guk, but I hate
> that place with a passion!!!!!

Cazic Thule. Killer exp off fanatics, gators and other mobs. And even
better, since rubi stopped spawning, it seems the place is usually
almost abandoned on most servers. We had a group of 5 in the temple area
last night and I got almost 3 bubbles of 32 in a couple of hours.
